  {
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I simply updated to the latest one at the time, so no deeper intention. In general I'd prefer upgrade over downgrade, but no idea what changes have gone in. Regressions from going .2 to .0 don't seem relevant IMO but don't know if we use `page.pause()` in our tests.",
