  {
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Yes, it causes the Nix image build to exit early if the Nix Playwright version does not match the one specified in package.json, as it cannot guarantee that `pnpm playwright:install` will be a no-op.\n\nInterestingly, I couldn't find us pre-caching or downloading the browsers in the standard dogfood image, which leads me to conclude that we are re-downloading Google Chrome and friends each time a workspace starts?",
